/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
/*                           617-624 ! Link Status x 8    nbcc       ! divides into 8 locations. Each location has 4 links. Each link is 4 bits that contains one of GDASTATE_*. */
/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
/*                           625-626 ! Link Questionable  nbcc       ! divides into 8 locations. Each location has 4 links. Each link is a bit indicating questionable. */
/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
/*                           627-642 ! CPU sts            nbcc       ! divides into 8 locations. Each location has 2 CPU statuses. Each CPU status is a word. */
/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
/*                               643 ! Data & Notif server OK nbcc   ! divides into 8 locations. Each location has 2 server OK, one for data one for notif. Each OK is 1 bit. */
/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
/*                               644 ! Lr Owned Last DeltaChange Date!  */
/*                                   ---------------------------------  */
